---
title: One-Pot Mexican Bacon & Kidney Bean Soup with Veggies, Cheddar Cheese & Corn Chips
description: This flavour combo is a beloved companion to many dishes like enchiladas, nachos and tacos. In the colder weather
though, why not try this tomato kidney bean, bacon and veggie delight in a soup? It won’t disappoint, in fact it may be the
new way to eat beans, veggies and cheese.
